<div><head>蕭子顯晉史草</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.2">明帝大寧三年十二月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.3">夜有赤氣如牙旗長短四面，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.4">西南最多。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.5">案天文占此為濛星，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.6">一曰刀星，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.7">亂之象。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.8">大興末及此再見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.9">王敦蘇峻之禍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.10">其應切矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-1a.11">《開元占經》八十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.2">王導妻妒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.3">導有眾妾在別館，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.4">妻知之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.5">持食刀將往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.6">公遽命駕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.7">患牛遲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.8">手捉麈尾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.9">以柄助打牛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.10">蔡謨聞之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.11">後詣王謂曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.12">「朝廷欲加公九錫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.13">王自敘謙志。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.14">蔡曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.15">「不聞餘物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.16">唯聞短轅犢車，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.17">長柄麈尾。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.18">導大慚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-2a.19">《太平廣記》二百四十六引《晉史》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.2">孝武太元十年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.3">謝安于步邱築埭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.4">後人為之召伯埭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.5">《御覽》二十八引《晉史》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.6">北狄各以部落為類，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.7">其人居塞內者有屠各、萎莎、羌渠、賀賴等種。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.8">《通鑑注晉紀》三引《晉史》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-3a.9">《通典》一百九十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-4a.2">鮮卑被髮左衽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-4a.3">故呼為索頭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1252_CHANT_001-4a.4">《通鑑注晉紀》二十四引蕭子顯曰。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
